00609 inline bool
00610 RouteSender::requestDone()
00611 {
00612    if ( ( m_requestSubRouteContainer.getSize() == 0 &&
00613           m_nbrOutstanding == 0 &&
00614           m_outgoingQueue.getCardinal() == 0 )
00615         || m_status != StringTable::OK )
00616       return true;
00617    else
00618       return false;
00619 }
